ton Villa]] (4)\n|[[Liverpool F.C.|Liverpool]]\n|[[Burnley F.C.|Burnley]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Steve Bloomer]] (Derby County)\n|23\n|-\n|align=center|[[1899\u20131900 Football League|1899\u20131900]]\n|[[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]] (5)\n|[[Sheffield United F.C.|Sheffield United]]\n|[[Sunderland A.F.C.|Sunderland]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Billy Garraty]] (Aston Villa)\n|27\n|-\n|align=center|[[1900\u201301 Football League|1900\u201301]]\n|[[Liverpool F.C.|Liverpool]]\n|[[Sunderland A.F.C.|Sunderland]]\n|[[Notts County F.C.|Notts County]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Steve Bloomer]] (Derby County)\n|23\n|-\n|align=center|[[1901\u201302 Football League|1901\u201302]]\n|[[Sunderland A.F.C.|Sunderland]] (4)\n|[[Everton F.C.|Everton]]\n|[[Newcastle United F.C.|Newcastle United]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jimmy Settle]] (Everton)\n|18\n|-\n|align=center|[[1902\u201303 Football League|1902\u201303]]\n|[[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|The Wednesday]]{{Ref label|Wednesday|8|a}}\n|[[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]]\n|[[Sunderland A.F.C.|Sunderland]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Sam Raybould]] (Liverpool)\n|31\n|-\n|align=center|[[1903\u201304 Football League|1903\u201304]]\n|[[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|The Wednesday]]{{Ref label|Wednesday|8|b}} (2)\n|[[Manchester City F.C.|Manchester City]]\n|[[Everton F.C.|Everton]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Steve Bloomer]] (Derby County)\n|20\n|-\n|align=center|[[1904\u201305 Football League|1904\u201305]]\n|[[Newcastle United F.C.|Newcastle United]]\n|[[Everton F.C.|Everton]]\n|[[Manchester City F.C.|Manchester City]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Arthur Brown (footballer, born 1885)|Arthur Brown]] (Sheffield United)\n|22\n|-\n|align=center|[[1905\u201306 Football League|1905\u201306]]\n|[[Liverpool F.C.|Liverpool]] (2)\n|[[Preston North End F.C.|Preston North End]]\n|[[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|The Wednesday]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Albert Shepherd]] (Bolton Wanderers)\n|26\n|-\n|align=center|[[1906\u201307 Football League|1906\u201307]]\n|[[Newcastle United F.C.|Newcastle United]] (2)