otter]] (The Wednesday)\n|37\n|-\n|align=center|[[1927\u201328 Football League|1927\u201328]]\n|[[Everton F.C.|Everton]] (3)\n|[[Huddersfield Town F.C.|Huddersfield Town]]\n|[[Leicester City F.C.|Leicester City]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Dixie Dean]] (Everton)\n|60\n|-\n|align=center|[[1928\u201329 Football League|1928\u201329]]\n|[[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|The Wednesday]]{{Ref label|Wednesday|8|c}} (3)\n|[[Leicester City F.C.|Leicester City]]\n|[[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]]\n|{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Dave Halliday]] (Sunderland)\n|43\n|-\n|align=center|[[1929\u201330 Football League|1929\u201330]]\n|[[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|Sheffield Wednesday]] (4)\n|[[Derby County F.C.|Derby County]]\n|[[Manchester City F.C.|Manchester City]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Vic Watson]] (West Ham United)\n|41\n|-\n|align=center|[[1930\u201331 Football League|1930\u201331]]\n|[[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]]\n|[[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]]\n|[[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|Sheffield Wednesday]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Tom Waring]] (Aston Villa)\n|49\n|-\n|align=center|[[1931\u201332 Football League|1931\u201332]]\n|[[Everton F.C.|Everton]] (4)\n|[[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]]\n|[[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|Sheffield Wednesday]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Dixie Dean]] (Everton)\n|44\n|-\n|align=center|[[1932\u201333 Football League|1932\u201333]]\n|[[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]] (2)\n|[[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]]\n|[[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|Sheffield Wednesday]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jack Bowers]] (Derby County)\n|35\n|-\n|align=center|[[1933\u201334 Football League|1933\u201334]]\n|[[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]] (3)\n|[[Huddersfield Town F.C.|Huddersfield Town]]\n|[[Tottenham Hotspur F.C.|Tottenham Hotspur]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jack Bowers]] (Derby County)\n|34\n|-\n|align=center|[[1934\u201335 Football League|1934\u201335]]\n|[[Arsenal F.C.|Arsenal]] (4)\n|[[Sunderland A.F.C.|Sunderland]]\n|[[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|Sheffield Wednesday]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ted Drake]] (Arsenal)\n|42\n|-\n|align=center|[[1935\u201336 Football 